In-Memory Database Maven Plug-in

  This plug-in provides the goals to launch and shutdown an embedded H2, HSQLDB or Apache Derby
  database that is running in-memory only. During launch the database can be seeded using
  DDL/DML scripts and/or DBUnit data sets.

* Goals Overview

~~  General Information about the goals.

  * {{{./run-mojo.html}inmemdb:run}} Start the in-memory database and optionally load data
    from DDL/DML scripts or DBUnit data sets.

  * {{{./stop-mojo.html}inmemdb:stop}} Stop the embedded server and drop the in-memory database.

